cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.AI 

The paper involves the use of data mining techniques to analyze customer data and predict prospective business sectors for lending in retail banking. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), data management (cs.DB), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper also deals with risk assessment in banking, which could fall under the sub-category of cryptography and security (cs.CR).
